In order to run this application, the following dependencies are required.

Java 1.8
Maven 3.5.0

Once the project has been downloaded, go to the project root directory via the command line
Once in the root directory of the project, you can run tests using the following maven command:

mvn clean install

If you want to run the application and see the list of products as well as the total price in json format then run the
following command:

mvn exec:java -Dexec.mainClass="com.sainsburys.Main"


This project has been developed using IntelliJ and you can import the project in intellJ as a maven project and run
all the tests as well as the main class from the IDE.